right now they're noshing pretty hard on the&nbsp;
acorns from our oak trees they live out here in&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:07.280 --> 00:02:14.640
a in an oak forest they've got about four acres&nbsp;
to forage from and that really makes our fall pork&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:21.040
quite special, my favorite cut is the blade steak so sometimes some people call it a butt chop&nbsp;&nbsp;

