that's fantastic there's so many benefits like we&nbsp;
because we're a small farm and a small business&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:02:55.280 --> 00:03:01.360
we are also supporting another small farmer who&nbsp;
makes our grain mix for us he's a grain grower&nbsp;&nbsp;

